# Law 0 (Omega): Integration -- The Center of the Cube

## The Supreme Law That Makes All Other Laws Possible

> **Number:** 0 (Omega)
> **Symbol:** Omega
> **Principle:** The universe has the capacity to order systems, from atoms to galaxies. When something separates, collapse occurs. Integration is the fundamental act of existence.
> **Author:** Ilver Villasmil
> **Date:** February 7, 2026

---

## 1. The 3x3x3 Cube: Where the Law Lives

### The Structure

A cube divided into 3x3x3 contains exactly 27 smaller cubes.

```
Total positions:      27
Exterior positions:   26 (visible, measurable, manifest)
Interior position:     1 (hidden, unmeasurable from outside)

ALPHA = 26/27 = 0.962963...  (the manifest)
BETA  = 1/27  = 0.037037...  (the center)
ALPHA + BETA  = 1             (the totality)
```

### The 26 Exterior Cubes

```
Face cubes:    6  (one exposed face)
Edge cubes:   12  (two exposed faces)
Corner cubes:  8  (three exposed faces)
Total:        26

These are what can be OBSERVED from outside.
These are what can be MEASURED.
These are what science traditionally studies.
These are ALPHA.
```

### The 1 Interior Cube

```
Exposed faces:  0
Visible from outside: NO
Touchable from any direction: NO
Removable without destroying the cube: NO

It has no exterior.
It cannot be observed from outside.
It can only be experienced from WITHIN.

This is BETA.
```

